explanations.reason: The paper focuses on a retrospective study of hospital-acquired pressure ulcers (PUs) and factors affecting their development, using statistical analysis (SPSS) and the Waterlow PU risk assessment tool. There is no mention of any machine learning techniques, algorithms, or models in the title or abstract. The study is purely clinical and statistical in nature, without any reference to the listed keywords related to machine learning, deep learning, or related methodologies.
